I am not sure whether it occurs with other form elements or not.</p>

<p>$element = new Zend_Form_Element_File('hoge');
$element-&gt;setDestination('/tmp')
        -&gt;addValidator('Size', false, 1024)
        -&gt;setName('foo')
        -&gt;addValidator('Extension', false, 'jpg,png,gif')
        ;</p>

